description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'The BEST way to start your day!  |  10-Minute Morning Yoga' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: In this quick but extremely beneficial routine, we will release tension, clear the mind, and connect to what matters most. Take 10 minutes to start the day on the right foot for better mental, emotional, and physical health. 

Stretch out stiffness, let’s energize for the day ahead! You won’t regret it.
